  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Ski Inclusive Plus offers great savings and the ultimate in convenience, maximum value and the reassurance of being able to budget for everything you need before your travel for your Ski holiday in advance. In many cases, further snacks such as packed lunch or afternoon tea &amp; coffee are also included, not to mention a wide range of leisure facilities. Our Ski Inclusive Plus holidays include all of the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Return flights &amp; transfers to resort</strong></li>
<li><strong>7 nights accommodation</strong></li>
<li><strong>7 night meals on either Full Board or Chalet Catering</strong></li>
<li><strong>Lift pass included</strong></li>
<li><strong>Ski &amp; boot Hire included</strong></li>
<li><strong>Lunch vouchers included</strong></li>
<li><strong>Free drinks with dinner</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><br />Choose from the Inghams ski inclusive properties below for simply outstanding value and fantastic savings!</p>
<h2><strong>Ski Inclusive Plus Accommodation</strong></h2>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;">
<p><img src="/media/13068678/inghams-ski-inclusive-chalet-hotel-elizabeth-kuehtai.jpg" alt="Chalet Hotel Elizabeth" data-udi="umb://media/d479c5591db2401483064751226b63b1" /><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/cb9e603bdf7a45d9beba674f542f9cb7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb9e603bdf7a45d9beba674f542f9cb7}" title="Chalet Hotel Elisabeth"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Chalet Hotel Elisabeth - Kühtai, Austria</span></a></p>
<p><span>The ultimate in skiing convenience with an unbeatable ski-in/ski-out, snow-sure location</span>.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/cb9e603bdf7a45d9beba674f542f9cb7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb9e603bdf7a45d9beba674f542f9cb7}" title="Chalet Hotel Elisabeth">View more information on Chalet Hotel Elisabeth &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;">
<p><img src="/media/13068682/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-village-club-du-soleil-flaine.jpg" alt="VCS Flaine" data-udi="umb://media/d0ddc946824c49d58bd050a8611a124e" /><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/d99e0ac379654e6197a2d3186341dfd6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d99e0ac379654e6197a2d3186341dfd6}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Village Club Du Soleil - Flaine, France</span></a></p>
<p><span>Located in the centre of Flaine Forum where access to the slopes is quick and easy...</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d99e0ac379654e6197a2d3186341dfd6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d99e0ac379654e6197a2d3186341dfd6}" title="Village Club du Soleil">View more information on Village Club Du Soleil &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;">
<p><img src="/media/13068684/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-village-club-du-soleil-montgenevre.jpg" alt="VCS Montgenevre" data-udi="umb://media/00e482ff92714ab68696fbba32889377" /><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Village Club Du Soleil - Montgenevre, France</span></a></p>
<p><span>Nestled on the border with Italy, the Montquitaine chairlift just 150m from the property, providing incredible access to the ski area...</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dc651bdab9c246e992a3222ec5b4e880}" title="Village Club du Soleil">View more information on Hotel Village Club Du Soleil &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;">
<p><img src="/media/13068686/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-village-club-du-soleil-morzine.jpg" alt="VCU Morzine" data-udi="umb://media/d02becb577be49c0b6070f93851d1da5" /><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Village Club Du Soleil - Morzine, France</span></a></p>
<p><span>An ideal choice for keen skiers and families alike. It has a great location with skiing from the Pleney piste and benefits from a sauna, steam room and whirlpool to relax in...</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb6e76f7c1484de0854c1ee7b9320d5a}" title="Village Club du Soleil">View more information on Hotel Village Club Du Soleil &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;">
<p><img src="/media/13068683/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-village-club-du-soleil-les-menuires.jpg" alt="VCS Les Menuires" data-udi="umb://media/7b62d25249b9424da80acc38881d535a" /><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1}" title="Village Club du Soleil"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Village Club Du Soleil - Les Menuires, France</span></a></p>
<p><span>Views from the property are stunning and can be enjoyed from the sun terrace or relax with a drink in the lounge after a long day on the slopes...</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a39e2c922ada4c2382fd21f3b4deefb1}" title="Village Club du Soleil">View more information on Hotel Village Club Du Soleil &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;">
<p><img src="/media/13068680/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-mottaret-meribel.jpg" alt="Le Mottaret Meribel" data-udi="umb://media/b75504981af24fb9b78034fe730609bd" /><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952}" title="Hotel Le Mottaret"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Le Mottaret - Meribel, France</span></a></p>
<p><span>Situated on the side of the piste in Méribel Mottaret 1800, the superb ski-inclusive Hotel Le Mottaret has everything you need for a week skiing</span>.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b03d11aa299c491296af4234c528b952}" title="Hotel Le Mottaret">View more information on Hotel Le Mottaret &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div><br />
<div> </div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;">
<p><img src="/media/13068681/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-princesa-parc-spa-arinsal.jpeg" alt="Princesa Parc Arinsal" data-udi="umb://media/aaa387cf07c948628fdc0c94ac0f98a2" /><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1}" title="Hotel Princesa Parc &amp; Spa"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Princesa Parc &amp; Spa - Arinsal</span></a></p>
<p><span>This resort hotel offers excellent facilities including a Wellness Spa with hydromassage pool</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2802a00933fe4625829b29d603f35ba1}" title="Hotel Princesa Parc &amp; Spa">View more information on Hotel Princesa &amp; Spa &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;">
<p><img src="/media/13068679/inghams-ski-inclusive-hotel-diana-parc-spa-arinsal.jpg" alt="Diana Parc Arinsal" data-udi="umb://media/7906dd1c255c4b8b9be15a6fb917e170" /><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f}" title="Diana Parc &amp; Spa Hotel"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;">Hotel Diana Parc &amp; Spa - Arinsal</span></a></p>
<p><span>TheHotel Diana &amp; Parc luxury resort hotel is Arinsal’s flagship property, offering excellent facilities...</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/893c41f0fc104a6a8f69cb426013148f}" title="Diana Parc &amp; Spa Hotel">View more information on Hotel Diana Parc &amp; Spa &gt;</a></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="min-height: 120px;"><strong>Prefer a more flexible catering option but looking for discounted ski equipment and lift pass? Why not choose our <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/ski-inclusive-bundles" target="_blank" title="Ski inclusive ski bundles">Ski Inclusive bundle</a> offer where you can save up to £128 per person &gt;</strong></div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
